<template>
  <VueMultiselect :options="users"/>
  <button>Premi</button>
</template>

<script>
import VueMultiselect from 'vue-multiselect'
import axios from "axios";
export default {
  name: "AdminRemoveLessons",
  components : {
    VueMultiselect
  },
  data(){
    return{
      users : ['Mario','Andrea','Giacomo']
    }
  },
  methods : {
    async fetchUsers(){
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('ServletAdminGetBookings',{params : {action : ''}});
      }catch (e){
        console.error(e.response);
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>
